                <DIV class="ReviewHeading">Book Description:</DIV>
                <span id="Label1">The international classic work of reference for anyone wishing to understand the factors governing the performance of a sailing boat.  Everyone interested in yacht design should read this book.  A new Appendix in this Third Edition presents a simple graphic method for predicting a yacht's behavior.</span>
              
</td></tr></table>
